OL,3,CInquiry into Crooked House rebuild
OL,4,Cpostponed after owners appeal
OL,6,FA public inquiry to decide whether the
OL,7,Fowners of the Crooked House near
OL,8,FDudley should rebuild the historic pub
OL,9,F"brick by brick", has been pushed back
OL,10,Fto next spring.
OL,12,FIt's following a decision by the
OL,13,FPlanning Inspectorate at the request
OL,14,Fof the owners.
OL,16,FThe 258-year-old pub in Himley, near
OL,17,FDudley, was reduced to rubble
OL,18,Ffollowing a fire on 5 August 2023.
