OL,3,CInquiry into Crooked House rebuild
OL,4,Cpostponed after owners appeal
OL,6,FBut they lodged an appeal in March and
OL,7,Fhave now won the right to postpone the
OL,8,Finquiry which was initially scheduled
OL,9,Ffor this summer.
OL,11,FThe inquiry has now been delayed until
OL,12,FSpring 2025 pending the outcome of
OL,13,Fpotential court actions related to a
OL,14,Frecent fire.
OL,16,FThe Planning Inspectorate acknowledged
OL,17,Fthe complexity of the case, noting
OL,18,Fthat resolving the planning
OL,19,Fenforcement appeal after the
OL,20,Fconclusion of any related court cases
OL,21,Fwould be ideal.
