OL,3,CInquiry into Crooked House rebuild
OL,4,Cpostponed after owners appeal
OL,6,FHowever, the Inspectorate also
OL,7,Femphasised that the delay should not
OL,8,Fbe indefinite, assuring that new dates
OL,9,Ffor the inquiry have been scheduled.
OL,11,FA Planning Inspectorate spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid:
OL,14,F"With regard to appeal reference
OL,15,F3341483, the Inspector has looked at
OL,16,Fthe Appellant's representations and
OL,17,Fagreed that it would be preferable to
OL,18,Fproceed with the Enforcement appeal
OL,19,Fafter any potential legal proceedings
OL,20,Fare concluded.
