OL,6,F"The Planning Inspectorate is not in a
OL,7,Fposition to comment further at this
OL,8,Fstage."
OL,10,FSix people have been with the fire,
OL,11,Fwhich is being treated as arson by
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,Fsays the suspects currently remain on
OL,15,Fconditional police bail as the
OL,16,Finvestigation continues.
OL,18,FSupporters argued that restoring the
OL,19,Fpub to its former glory was essential
OL,20,Ffor preserving the cultural and
OL,21,Fhistorical heritage of the area.
